00:15:12,478 --> 00:15:15,981
THE LEGION OF DECENCY NOT ONLY
RATED MOVIES AS TO CONTENT,

208
00:15:15,981 --> 00:15:18,984
BUT THREATENED MASSIVE BOYCOTTS.

209
00:15:19,985 --> 00:15:23,989
HOLLYWOOD PROMISED
TO PLAY BY THE RULES.

210
00:15:23,989 --> 00:15:26,992
THE HAYS CODE JUST...

211
00:15:26,992 --> 00:15:30,495
SET UP A SERIES OF RULES
THAT WERE INVIOLABLE.

212
00:15:42,508 --> 00:15:45,010
[ Tomlin ]
CODE DIRECTOR JOE BREEN...

213
00:15:45,010 --> 00:15:48,513
RAN HOLLYWOOD'S CENSORSHIP
MACHINERY FOR OVER TWO DECADES.

214
00:15:49,014 --> 00:15:53,018
HE WAS AUTHORIZED
TO CHANGE WORDS, PERSONALITIES AND PLOTS.

215
00:15:55,020 --> 00:15:58,023
A NOVEL ABOUT A SEXUALLY
CONFUSED ALCOHOLIC...

216
00:15:58,023 --> 00:16:01,526
BECAME A MOVIE ABOUT AN
ALCOHOLIC WITH WRITER'S BLOCK.

217
00:16:03,529 --> 00:16:06,031
A NOVEL ABOUT GAY BASHING
AND MURDER...

218
00:16:06,031 --> 00:16:10,035
BECAME A MOVIE
ABOUT ANTI-SEMITISM AND MURDER.

219
00:16:10,536 --> 00:16:13,038
OUR AMERICAN PEOPLE
ARE A PRETTY HOMELY...

220
00:16:13,038 --> 00:16:15,540
AND WHOLESOME CROWD.

221
00:16:15,541 --> 00:16:18,544
COCKEYED PHILOSOPHIES OF LIFE,

222
00:16:18,544 --> 00:16:23,549
UGLY SEX SITUATIONS, CHEAP JOKES
AND DIRTY DIALOGUE...

223
00:16:23,549 --> 00:16:25,551
ARE NOT WANTED.

224
00:16:25,551 --> 00:16:28,053
THE DECENT PEOPLE
DON'T LIKE THIS SORT OF STUFF,

225
00:16:28,053 --> 00:16:31,556
AND IT IS OUR JOB TO SEE TO IT
THAT THEY GET NONE OF IT.

226
00:16:31,557 --> 00:16:35,060
HAVE YOU EVER
MODELED BEFORE ? NO, I HAVEN'T.

227
00:16:35,060 --> 00:16:38,563
I'M DOING A STUDY OF A YOUNG
GIRL'S HEAD AND SHOULDERS.

228
00:16:38,564 --> 00:16:41,066
YOU WON'T OBJECT TO REMOVING
YOUR BLOUSE, WILL YOU ?

229
00:16:41,066 --> 00:16:43,568
NO, I GUESS NOT.

230
00:16:43,569 --> 00:16:45,070
YOU CAN GET READY
BEHIND THAT SCREEN.

231
00:16:45,571 --> 00:16:47,573
[ Tomlin ]
THE PRODUCTION CODE...

232
00:16:47,573 --> 00:16:51,076
DIDN'T ERASE HOMOSEXUALS
FROM THE SCREEN; IT JUST MADE THEM HARDER TO FIND.

233
00:16:51,076 --> 00:16:55,580
AND NOW THEY HAD A NEW IDENTITY
AS COLD-BLOODED VILLAINS.

234
00:16:55,581 --> 00:16:58,584
I'M READY NOW.

235
00:17:02,588 --> 00:17:06,091
- YOU'LL WANT THESE
PULLED DOWN, WON'T YOU ? - YES.

236
00:17:10,095 --> 00:17:14,099
WHY ARE YOU LOOKING AT ME
THAT WAY ?  WON'T I DO ?

237
00:17:14,600 --> 00:17:17,102
YES, YOU'LL
DO VERY WELL INDEED.

238
00:17:18,604 --> 00:17:20,606
DO YOU LIKE JEWELS, LILY ?

239
00:17:20,606 --> 00:17:23,609
THIS IS VERY OLD
AND VERY BEAUTIFUL.

240
00:17:23,609 --> 00:17:26,612
<i>I'LL SHOW IT TO YOU.</i>

241
00:17:29,114 --> 00:17:32,617
I DON'T THINK
I'LL POSE TONIGHT.  I--

242
00:17:32,618 --> 00:17:35,120
