IF YOU DON'T MIND.

243
00:17:36,121 --> 00:17:38,623
PLEASE DON'T
COME ANY CLOSER !

244
00:17:42,127 --> 00:17:44,129
<i>[ Screaming ]</i>

245
00:17:50,135 --> 00:17:52,637
I DIDN'T EXPECT TO SEE YOU,
MRS. DANVERS.

246
00:17:53,138 --> 00:17:56,641
A WINDOW WASN'T CLOSED,
AND I CAME TO FASTEN IT.

247
00:17:56,642 --> 00:18:00,145
WHY DID YOU SAY THAT ?
I CLOSED IT BEFORE I LEFT THE ROOM.

248
00:18:00,646 --> 00:18:02,147
YOU OPENED IT YOURSELF,
DIDN'T YOU ?

249
00:18:02,648 --> 00:18:04,149
[ Bright ]
REBECCA <i>IS ONE OF THE MOVIES...</i>

250
00:18:04,650 --> 00:18:08,654
IN WHICH THE WORD HOMOSEXUALITY
OR LESBIANISM <i>IS NEVER UTTERED.</i>

251
00:18:08,654 --> 00:18:11,657
BUT THERE'S THIS ONE SCENE...

252
00:18:11,657 --> 00:18:15,661
THAT REALLY STANDS OUT
FOR A GAY AUDIENCE.

253
00:18:15,661 --> 00:18:18,664
AND THAT IS, REBECCA IS DEAD.

254
00:18:18,664 --> 00:18:23,669
SHE WAS THE BEAUTIFUL WOMAN
WHO IS MYSTERIOUSLY NOT ON THE SCENE ANY LONGER.

255
00:18:23,669 --> 00:18:26,672
AND HER FORMER HOUSEKEEPER,
MRS. DANVERS,

256
00:18:26,672 --> 00:18:30,175
IS OBSESSED WITH HER,
EVEN AFTER HER DEATH.

257
00:18:30,175 --> 00:18:33,178
THIS IS WHERE I
KEEP ALL HER CLOTHES.

258
00:18:34,179 --> 00:18:36,681
YOU WOULD LIKE TO SEE THEM,
WOULDN'T YOU ?

259
00:18:47,693 --> 00:18:50,195
FEEL THIS.

260
00:18:50,195 --> 00:18:53,198
IT WAS A CHRISTMAS PRESENT
FROM MR. DeWINTER.

261
00:18:56,702 --> 00:19:00,205
HE WAS ALWAYS GIVING HER
EXPENSIVE GIFTS THE WHOLE YEAR ROUND.

262
00:19:02,207 --> 00:19:05,210
I KEEP HER UNDERWEAR
ON THIS SIDE.

263
00:19:07,212 --> 00:19:11,716
THEY WERE MADE SPECIALLY
FOR HER BY THE NUNS IN THE CONVENT OF ST. CLAIR.

264
00:19:13,719 --> 00:19:16,722
SHE OPENS THE UNDERWEAR DRAWER !

265
00:19:16,722 --> 00:19:18,724
IT'S SO SENSUOUS.

266
00:19:18,724 --> 00:19:22,227
LOOK.  YOU CAN SEE
MY HAND THROUGH IT.

267
00:19:26,231 --> 00:19:30,735
THE GUYS WHO RAN THAT CODE
WEREN'T ROCKET SCIENTISTS. THEY MISSED A LOT OF STUFF.

268
00:19:31,236 --> 00:19:34,739
AND IF A DIRECTOR WAS SUBTLE
ENOUGH AND CLEVER ENOUGH, THEY GOT AROUND IT.

269
00:19:36,241 --> 00:19:38,743
WHAT'LL IT COST
TO BE ON THE SAFE SIDE ?

270
00:19:38,744 --> 00:19:40,746
OKAY.  GO AHEAD.

271
00:19:46,752 --> 00:19:49,755
GARDENIA.
QUICK, DARLING. IN WITH HIM.

272
00:19:49,755 --> 00:19:53,258
WE KNOW PETER LORRE'S GAY
IN THE MALTESE FALCON EVEN BEFORE WE SEE HIM.

273
00:19:53,759 --> 00:19:57,763
