WHY, YOU'RE
JUST A KID YOURSELF.

315
00:22:13,899 --> 00:22:17,402
SO LONG, MARIE.
GOOD-BYE, ANNE. THANK YOU.

316
00:22:17,402 --> 00:22:20,905
