GET ACQUAINTED, HONEY.

317
00:22:20,906 --> 00:22:24,409
YOU MAY BE A NUMBER
TO THE OTHERS, BUT NOT TO ME.

318
00:22:25,410 --> 00:22:29,414
SIT DOWN IN THIS CHAIR.
IT'S KIND OF ROOMY.

319
00:22:30,916 --> 00:22:33,418
[ Bright ]
THERE'S SUPPOSED TO BE A SOCIAL MESSAGE TO ALL THIS.

320
00:22:33,418 --> 00:22:37,922
ISN'T IT TERRIBLE
