321
00:22:37,923 --> 00:22:40,425
ISN'T IT TERRIBLE
FOR A WOMAN TO GO HARD ?

322
00:22:40,425 --> 00:22:45,430
WHAT'S YOUR NAME ?
HOW'D YOU HURT YOUR HAND ?

323
00:22:45,430 --> 00:22:49,934
I'M A BIG GIRL, AND THIS ISN'T
MY FIRST YEAR AWAY FROM HOME.

324
00:22:49,935 --> 00:22:52,437
MY NAME IS MARIE ALLEN.

325
00:22:52,437 --> 00:22:55,440
IF I SAID NO TO KITTY,
I'M SURE NOT GONNA SAY YES TO YOU.

326
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:57,442
