328
00:23:01,446 --> 00:23:04,449
♪ I MAY BE WRONG BUT ♪

329
00:23:04,449 --> 00:23:06,951
[ Bright ]
IN YOUNG MAN WITH A HORN, WE HAVE ONE OF MY FAVORITE...

330
00:23:06,952 --> 00:23:10,455
LESBIAN GLAMOUR SYMBOLS.
JO'S INTERESTING, ISN'T SHE ?

331
00:23:10,956 --> 00:23:12,958
