BECAUSE SHE GETS UP IN THE MORNING,

336
00:23:26,972 --> 00:23:30,475
AND SHE HAS NO IDEA
WHAT'S GOING TO HAPPEN TO HER NEXT.

337
00:23:30,475 --> 00:23:33,478
<i>I'M DYING TO SEE THE REST</i>
<i>OF YOUR SKETCHES.</i>

338
00:23:33,478 --> 00:23:36,481
WE'LL HAVE DINNER OUT
AND THEN GO BACK TO MY PLACE.

339
00:23:39,484 --> 00:23:41,986
HOW NICE OF YOU
