I TOLD YOU ABOUT HER,
THE GIRL WHO PAINTS SO WELL.

342
00:23:47,993 --> 00:23:50,996
HOW DO YOU DO ?
HOW DO YOU DO ?

343
00:23:52,998 --> 00:23:55,500
SEE YOU AT 9:00,
THEN, AMY. FINE.

344
00:23:55,500 --> 00:23:57,502
IT'S BEEN A WONDERFUL PARTY.

345
00:23:57,502 --> 00:24:00,505
