348
00:24:05,510 --> 00:24:08,012
WHAT A SWELL COMBINATION
WE WERE !

349
00:24:08,013 --> 00:24:10,015
YOU SAID YOU WANTED
EXPERIENCES, AMY.

350
00:24:10,015 --> 00:24:13,018
WELL, HERE'S ONE FOR YOU.
I'M LEAVING YOU.

351
00:24:13,018 --> 00:24:15,020
I'D LIKE TO KILL YOU !

352
00:24:16,021 --> 00:24:19,024
