A KIND OF PARADISE NOW.

358
00:24:38,043 --> 00:24:40,545
BUT AT THE TIME THAT
WE WERE LIVING THROUGH IT,

359
00:24:40,545 --> 00:24:43,548
WE THOUGHT THAT WE
WERE IN A DECADE...

360
00:24:43,548 --> 00:24:48,052
OF SUCH TOWERING DULLNESS
AND STUPIDITY.

361
00:24:48,053 --> 00:24:51,056
I WANT TO BE PROUD
OF HIM.

362
00:24:51,056 --> 00:24:53,558
THAT'S WHY I HAD HIM
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

363
00:24:53,558 --> 00:24:56,561
BUT HE MAKES IT
SO DIFFICULT FOR ME.

364
00:24:56,561 --> 00:24:58,563
