WHAT HE WANTS TO BE,

365
00:24:59,064 --> 00:25:02,567
AND I HAVE TO TELL THEM
THAT HE HASN'T MADE UP HIS MIND.

366
00:25:02,567 --> 00:25:06,070
BECAUSE I JUST WON'T TELL
THEM THAT HE WANTS TO BE A--

367
00:25:06,071 --> 00:25:08,073
A FOLKSINGER.

368
00:25:08,073 --> 00:25:10,575
<i>♪ THE GRIEF ♪</i>

369
00:25:10,575 --> 00:25:15,580
♪ OF LOVE ENDURES ♪

370
00:25:15,580 --> 00:25:19,083
[ Tomlin ]
IN '50s AMERICA, MASCULINITY RULED.

371
00:25:19,084 --> 00:25:22,087
SEEMING GAY WAS ALMOST AS BAD
AS BEING GAY,

372
00:25:22,087 --> 00:25:24,589
SO A MAN HAD TO WATCH
HIS EVERY STEP.

373
00:25:24,589 --> 00:25:26,591
LOOK, TOM,
THE WAY YOU WALK--

374
00:25:26,591 --> 00:25:28,593
OH !
I'M JUST TRYING TO HELP YOU !

375
00:25:28,593 --> 00:25:31,095
