FORGET IT !

377
00:25:35,600 --> 00:25:37,602
AL ?
YEAH ?

378
00:25:37,602 --> 00:25:40,605
[ Dyer ]
TEA AND SYMPATHY <i>IS DEFINITELY</i> <i>ABOUT BEING HOMOSEXUAL.</i>

379
00:25:40,605 --> 00:25:44,108
I'M SORRY.
TELL ME HOW I WALK.

380
00:25:44,109 --> 00:25:47,612
IT'S A FILM THAT'S ABOUT
CURING HOMOSEXUALITY.

381
00:25:47,612 --> 00:25:50,114
AND THE SIGNS OF HOMOSEXUALITY
ARE EFFEMINACY.

382
00:25:50,115 --> 00:25:53,118
WELL, THEN, YOU WALK.
LET ME WATCH YOU.

383
00:25:53,118 --> 00:25:57,122
I-I NEVER NOTICED
HOW YOU WALK. OKAY.

384
00:26:09,134 --> 00:26:11,136
DO IT AGAIN.

385
00:26:11,136 --> 00:26:14,139
