ABOUT THIS ! DO YOU THINK I WOULD ?

386
00:26:17,142 --> 00:26:19,644
WE KNOW THE SAL MINEO CHARACTER
IS GAY...

387
00:26:19,644 --> 00:26:22,647
PARTLY BECAUSE HE HAS
A PICTURE OF ALAN LADD IN HIS LOCKER,

388
00:26:22,647 --> 00:26:26,150
BUT ALSO FROM HIS ADORATION...

389
00:26:26,651 --> 00:26:28,653
OF THE JAMES DEAN CHARACTER.

390
00:26:41,666 --> 00:26:44,168
HEY, YOU WANT TO COME HOME
WITH ME ?  THERE'S NOBODY HOME AT MY HOUSE.

391
00:26:44,169 --> 00:26:47,172
HECK, I'M NOT TIRED.
ARE YOU ?

392
00:26:47,172 --> 00:26:49,174
SEE, I DON'T HAVE TOO MANY
PEOPLE I CAN TALK TO.

393
00:26:49,174 --> 00:26:51,176
WHO HAS ?

394
00:26:51,176 --> 00:26:56,181
