396
00:26:58,683 --> 00:27:03,688
BUT ANY FILM IS
AT THE SAME TIME...

397
00:27:03,688 --> 00:27:07,692
AN EXPRESSION OF A WRITER,

398
00:27:07,692 --> 00:27:10,194
AND IT'S AN OFFERING...

399
00:27:10,195 --> 00:27:12,197
TO AN AUDIENCE...

400
00:27:12,197 --> 00:27:14,199
TO CREATE THEIR OWN FILM.

401
00:27:14,199 --> 00:27:16,201
ARE YOU COLD ?

402
00:27:16,201 --> 00:27:20,705
[ Stern ]
REBEL <i>WAS ABOUT TENDERNESS,</i> <i>INTIMACY.</i>

403
00:27:21,206 --> 00:27:25,210
IT WAS AN ATTEMPT TO WIDEN
THE PERMISSION TO LOVE...

404
00:27:25,210 --> 00:27:28,213
WHEN MEN WERE SUPPOSED TO BE
ONE WAY WITH EACH OTHER.

405
00:27:28,213 --> 00:27:32,717
CAN I KEEP IT ?
WELL, WHAT DO YOU THINK ? HERE.

406
00:27:35,220 --> 00:27:38,223
I THINK IF I WERE WRITING
THAT SCRIPT AGAIN TODAY...

407
00:27:38,223 --> 00:27:41,726
THAT I WOULD BE MUCH MORE
SPECIFIC ABOUT PLATO.

408
00:27:41,726 --> 00:27:45,730
I WOULD LET HIM
BE AN OUTCAST...

409
00:27:45,730 --> 00:27:49,233
