THOUGHT HE WAS A FAGGOT,

410
00:27:49,234 --> 00:27:53,738
<i>AND LET HIS ISOLATION</i>
<i>COME FROM THAT OPINION.</i>

411
00:27:56,241 --> 00:27:58,243
